summary:
I am a 3rd year student in the "Logistics Management" programme in Fontys University for Applied Sciences, Venlo. 
In my course I am being taught various logistics and economics subjects providing me with broad knowledge of the business world of logistics both on theoretical and practical level. However, my interest lies in controlling and managing road transport 
I have 8-month work experience in a logistics company as a warehouse employee. In the future I would like to grow to a logistics manager dealing with road transportation.
